Recommended proposal: the fast + lean (runtime-first) solution.

This is the canonical answer for the challenge: the fastest runtime that still keeps
memory low. Replace this file with the implementation and rename it with the selected
language extension (for example solution.cpp, solution.rs, solution.go, ...).

Two more proposals are required alongside it:
- solution-runtime.{ext} - the asymptotic-speed / early-exit extreme.
- solution-memory.{ext}  - the minimum-memory extreme.

Each proposal may use a different language, chosen by performance analysis. See
docs/challenge-format.md.
